                div.form-group
                    label(for="password") <你的密码呐 />
                    input.form-control#password(type="password" placeholder="叽里咕噜...")

                div(class="btn-group btn-group-justified")
                    a#go-pikachu(type="button" data-complete-text="皮卡丘成功出仓..." data-loading-text="精灵球正在出货..."
                        class="btn btn-warning") 去吧，皮卡丘！
                    a(type="button" class="btn btn-danger") 初音未来の消失

                div(class="btn-group btn-group-justified" style="margin-top: 10px;")
                    a(type="button" class="btn btn-info") 和我签订契约，成为魔法码畜吧 ／人◕‿‿◕人＼
            div.col-md-3